        <briefdescription>
<para>This function zeroizes the BBRAM. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS Success in Zeroization of BBRAM.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XNVM_BBRAM_ERROR_ZEROIZE_TIMEOUT If Timed out during BBRAM zeroization </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
