<listitem><para>Write 1 to BBRAM_CTRL register. Wait for BBRAM_ZEROIZED bit to set in BBRAM_STATUS register with timeout of 1 second. If timed out return timeout error. Return XST_SUCCESS.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
